 the star formation timescale traced by GALEX and Spitzer\ndata, while SCUBA-2 preferentially traces the densest gas within these regions,\nwhich likely forms stars on shorter timescales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2023 17:50:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
