ared with the state-of-the-art large-scale multi-node GNN training systems\nsuch as P3 and DistDGL, our CPU-FPGA design achieves up to 5.27x speedup using\na single node.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 01:12:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-02"}
