f an almost\nvertical photometric sequence in the Gaia colour-magnitude diagram is a safe\nway to identify young open clusters. Automated methods for the determination of\ncluster properties give approximate solutions, but are still subject to some\ndifficulties. There is some evidence suggesting that artificial intelligence\nsystems may systematically underestimate extinction, which may impact in the\nage determination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 12:49:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-02"}
