s and\nestablish the solvability of the corresponding adjoint systems in order to\nderive the associated first-order necessary optimality conditions for the\noptimal control problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 13:23:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-02"}
