 improving the COP of the cooling\nmode are significantly lower.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 15:16:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 15:36:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-07"}
