eraction rules. We believe that PINE\nand its application presented here provide a mechanistic understanding of\nemergent dynamics important in cellular and soft matter reorganization,\nself-organization, and pattern formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2023 20:54:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
